metadata.name: Spill your guts
metadata.description:
PNG 3800 x 3800

"Spill your guts" is a digital artwork created by the artist Indi Sulta.  
Using various digital methods, mainly digital painting and AI image2image generation. All processed through Photoshop and Sketchbook.

This is a personal work, portraying a person with their guts spilled.  
"Spill your guts" is an idiomatic expression, meaning to divulge secrets or to talk freely/uninhibitedly. The writing on the walls here are directly from the artist speaking freely of their situation at the time of making this piece of art, written in their native tongue, Icelandic.
